data.description: SELLER WILL CONTRIBUTE UP TO $10,000 IN BUYERS CLOSING COSTS. 4.7 acres of beautiful views! Includes a fenced pasture, paved driveway, and LOW county taxes. 3 bedroom 2 bath, 1917 sq.ft. Features a living room and family room, as well as an office/den that is currently being used as a 4th bedroom. Primary suite has 2 sinks, a garden tub and a walk in shower. Vaulted ceilings throughout the house. Roof was replaced in 2022. Excellent shared well with association. Beautiful hunting property! If you are looking for privacy in a convenient location, this may be the home for you!
